WEBVTT

00:03:55.040 --> 00:03:57.230
Well, good evening, family. Thank you

00:03:57.240 --> 00:03:59.750
for joining me again today. I just

00:03:59.760 --> 00:04:01.150
want to tell y'all thank you for joining

00:04:01.160 --> 00:04:03.230
us and praying with us and being

00:04:03.240 --> 00:04:04.670
here so promptly.

00:04:04.680 --> 00:04:06.910
I'm going to go over some things

00:04:06.920 --> 00:04:08.790
from what the Lord showed us in this last

00:04:08.800 --> 00:04:10.630
video, but I want to say this right off

00:04:10.640 --> 00:04:12.310
the bat:

00:04:12.320 --> 00:04:14.270
I have to apologize. I was corrected by

00:04:14.280 --> 00:04:17.789
the Spirit of the Lord today. I

00:04:17.799 --> 00:04:19.910
went about last night, some of the things

00:04:19.920 --> 00:04:22.310
I said and how I criticized

00:04:22.320 --> 00:04:24.070
President Trump,

00:04:24.080 --> 00:04:26.030
and the Lord said I dishonored him.

00:04:26.040 --> 00:04:28.950
I want to say this: I apologize

00:04:28.950 --> 00:04:28.960
for

00:04:28.960 --> 00:04:32.230
my opinion and how I present myself

00:04:32.800 --> 00:04:34.870
and some of the things I say

00:04:34.880 --> 00:04:37.310
when I criticize him.

00:04:37.310 --> 00:04:37.320
Because

00:04:37.320 --> 00:04:39.630
of

00:04:39.640 --> 00:04:41.070
things that the Lord had talked to me

00:04:41.080 --> 00:04:44.630
privately about, I brought them up publicly,

00:04:44.640 --> 00:04:45.830
and there were things that I shouldn't

00:04:45.840 --> 00:04:47.550
have said. Me and Him,

00:04:47.560 --> 00:04:49.510
we have these

00:04:49.520 --> 00:04:51.830
conversations, but what we say doesn't

00:04:51.840 --> 00:04:53.870
mean it's for the public. Does that

00:04:53.880 --> 00:04:56.150
make sense?

00:04:56.160 --> 00:04:58.270
Like my wife and I

00:04:58.280 --> 00:04:59.909
have conversations we don't bring out in

00:04:59.919 --> 00:05:01.070
public;

00:05:01.080 --> 00:05:02.790
you just have private

00:05:02.800 --> 00:05:04.230
conversations.

00:05:04.240 --> 00:05:06.350
That's the way it is with the Lord. There

00:05:06.350 --> 00:05:06.360
are

00:05:06.360 --> 00:05:07.990
certain things I said about

00:05:08.000 --> 00:05:10.350
his voting and the past

00:05:10.360 --> 00:05:13.270
that I owe apologies

00:05:13.270 --> 00:05:13.280
for,

00:05:13.280 --> 00:05:15.190
and the Lord corrected me very sternly.

00:05:15.200 --> 00:05:16.950
He said, 'Brandon,

00:05:16.960 --> 00:05:19.430
the more your platform has

00:05:19.440 --> 00:05:22.390
influence and the more it grows, you're

00:05:22.400 --> 00:05:24.110
going to be held accountable more and

00:05:24.120 --> 00:05:26.070
more for what you say.

00:05:26.080 --> 00:05:27.550
You can't just flippantly say

00:05:27.560 --> 00:05:29.870
things out of your mouth.

00:05:31.320 --> 00:05:33.190
This is a public forum; there

00:05:33.190 --> 00:05:33.200
are

00:05:33.200 --> 00:05:35.470
millions of people

00:05:35.470 --> 00:05:35.480
watching.'So,

00:05:35.480 --> 00:05:37.750
for everybody in the government,

00:05:37.760 --> 00:05:39.150
I'm going to tell you this: I apologize

00:05:39.150 --> 00:05:39.160
for

00:05:39.160 --> 00:05:40.750
how I handle myself sometimes. You

00:05:40.760 --> 00:05:42.710
know what I'm learning? I'm growing and

00:05:42.710 --> 00:05:42.720
I am

00:05:42.720 --> 00:05:44.830
immature in how I handle some things.

00:05:44.840 --> 00:05:47.070
I just want to say that I ask

00:05:47.080 --> 00:05:48.790
you to overlook certain

00:05:48.800 --> 00:05:50.510
things. I'm

00:05:50.510 --> 00:05:50.520
growing—growing

00:05:50.520 --> 00:05:52.150
pains is what I want to call

00:05:52.160 --> 00:05:54.550
it. Was that anybody

00:05:54.560 --> 00:05:55.790
else telling me to say that? No, it was the

00:05:55.800 --> 00:05:57.630
Holy Spirit. He corrected me very

00:05:57.630 --> 00:05:57.640
sternly

00:05:57.640 --> 00:05:59.750
today. I was out letting my

00:05:59.760 --> 00:06:02.510
dog go to the bathroom,

00:06:02.520 --> 00:06:06.750
and

00:06:06.760 --> 00:06:08.350
the Lord corrected me.

00:06:08.360 --> 00:06:10.790
It was a very

00:06:10.800 --> 00:06:12.310
heavy correction.

00:06:12.320 --> 00:06:15.710
So, anytime the Lord corrects me to

00:06:15.720 --> 00:06:18.150
the strength that He did today, I want

00:06:18.160 --> 00:06:21.030
to always be quick to repent and make it

00:06:21.040 --> 00:06:22.150
right.

00:06:22.160 --> 00:06:23.670
I don't even know if I could make

00:06:23.680 --> 00:06:25.230
that right other than just say,

00:06:25.240 --> 00:06:27.150
'Listen, I was

00:06:27.150 --> 00:06:27.160
wrong.'My

00:06:27.160 --> 00:06:30.070
opinion and the conversations

00:06:30.080 --> 00:06:32.110
I have with the Father just need

00:06:32.110 --> 00:06:32.120
to—I

00:06:32.120 --> 00:06:34.870
need to learn how to filter better. So,

00:06:34.880 --> 00:06:36.630
like I said,

00:06:36.640 --> 00:06:38.750
with all that being said, I pray for

00:06:38.760 --> 00:06:40.909
grace from all y'all. There

00:06:40.909 --> 00:06:40.919
was

00:06:40.919 --> 00:06:42.950
not even anybody who said

00:06:42.960 --> 00:06:44.990
anything. It was interesting; it

00:06:45.000 --> 00:06:47.510
was just from the Lord.

00:06:48.600 --> 00:06:50.870
But I'm always quick to make it

00:06:50.880 --> 00:06:52.230
right.

00:06:52.240 --> 00:06:54.110
Be quick to repent and turn from things

00:06:54.120 --> 00:06:56.390
when the Holy Spirit corrects you.

00:06:56.400 --> 00:06:58.909
In doing so, I've

00:06:58.919 --> 00:07:00.750
continued to do that. That's why I

00:07:00.760 --> 00:07:02.150
believe that

00:07:02.150 --> 00:07:02.160
if

00:07:02.160 --> 00:07:03.630
you keep a heart right before Him, He'll

00:07:03.640 --> 00:07:05.190
keep using you.

00:07:08.520 --> 00:07:10.870
Now,

00:07:10.880 --> 00:07:12.710
praying over President Trump's

00:07:12.720 --> 00:07:14.190
decisions

00:07:14.190 --> 00:07:14.200
and

00:07:14.200 --> 00:07:17.590
the council,

00:07:17.600 --> 00:07:20.350
when I heard him

00:07:20.360 --> 00:07:23.670
talking about Taiwan

00:07:23.670 --> 00:07:23.680
and

00:07:23.680 --> 00:07:27.070
China—can

00:07:27.080 --> 00:07:28.950
you make sure what's that beeping

00:07:28.960 --> 00:07:31.110
noise in the back? It's really

00:07:31.120 --> 00:07:33.390
loud.

00:07:33.400 --> 00:07:35.550
Do you hear the beep, beep, beep?

00:07:38.040 --> 00:07:40.390
When I heard

00:07:41.880 --> 00:07:44.310
in the meeting what was being said,

00:07:44.320 --> 00:07:47.670
President Trump confirmed what we heard

00:07:47.680 --> 00:07:49.430
in the Spirit

00:07:49.440 --> 00:07:52.190
24 hours ago. He

00:07:52.200 --> 00:07:54.590
confirmed it today in the news.

00:07:54.600 --> 00:07:58.790
It was told

00:07:58.800 --> 00:08:00.510
that Xi

00:08:00.510 --> 00:08:00.520
Jinping

00:08:00.520 --> 00:08:04.950
asked him

00:08:11.990 --> 00:08:12.000
directly—the

00:08:18.960 --> 00:08:20.430
president of China

00:08:20.440 --> 00:08:21.990
asked him

00:08:22.000 --> 00:08:24.190
directly—'Will

00:08:24.200 --> 00:08:27.110
you stand in resistance if we take

00:08:27.120 --> 00:08:29.230
Taiwan?'and

00:08:29.240 --> 00:08:31.830
President Trump would not answer.

00:08:31.840 --> 00:08:33.390
And you're about to hear that. So, what

00:08:33.400 --> 00:08:34.950
did I hear?

00:08:36.560 --> 00:08:37.990
I heard

00:08:38.000 --> 00:08:40.230
that China was going to take Taiwan as

00:08:40.240 --> 00:08:42.029
we took

00:08:42.039 --> 00:08:45.230
Cuba in the days ahead.

00:08:45.240 --> 00:08:47.670
I saw the President

00:08:47.680 --> 00:08:51.430
liberating Cuba in the

00:08:51.440 --> 00:08:53.310
days ahead,

00:08:53.320 --> 00:08:55.030
and that there would be a financial

00:08:55.040 --> 00:08:57.829
blessing over Cuba for the first time in

00:08:57.839 --> 00:08:59.430
decades.

00:08:59.440 --> 00:09:01.350
They would liberate the

00:09:01.360 --> 00:09:04.350
tyrant government that has been

00:09:04.360 --> 00:09:07.630
over them, and Rubio will slay his tens

00:09:07.640 --> 00:09:10.510
of thousands and the

00:09:10.520 --> 00:09:13.950
chameleon will slay his thousands, and

00:09:13.960 --> 00:09:15.829
there will be jealousy between the

00:09:15.839 --> 00:09:18.470
two

00:09:18.480 --> 00:09:20.829
as one rises up in the polls and people

00:09:20.839 --> 00:09:24.190
say, 'We want him. We want David

00:09:24.200 --> 00:09:27.870
as our president

00:09:27.870 --> 00:09:27.880
next.'The

00:09:27.880 --> 00:09:30.310
one will be jealous of

00:09:30.320 --> 00:09:32.390
it and he'll have his thousands,

00:09:32.400 --> 00:09:33.590
but the one will have his tens of

00:09:33.600 --> 00:09:36.150
thousands. And I saw him becoming very

00:09:36.160 --> 00:09:39.510
polished in the days ahead, Rubio.

00:09:39.520 --> 00:09:42.310
And I saw an anointing on him,

00:09:42.320 --> 00:09:45.230
and I saw Byron, the black man

00:09:45.240 --> 00:09:46.950
that has the

00:09:46.950 --> 00:09:46.960
beard—I

00:09:46.960 --> 00:09:49.110
saw that God was putting an

00:09:49.120 --> 00:09:51.870
anointing on this man.

00:09:51.880 --> 00:09:54.390
And I saw the number 25%. The Lord

00:09:54.400 --> 00:09:56.230
said, 'There are things that need to be

00:09:56.240 --> 00:10:01.830
corrected, but it's not much.

00:10:01.840 --> 00:10:05.350
I will use this man in the days

00:10:05.350 --> 00:10:05.360
ahead.'Do

00:10:05.360 --> 00:10:07.470
you know who I'm talking about?

00:10:07.480 --> 00:10:08.830
You can show his picture if you want,

00:10:08.840 --> 00:10:11.590
but I saw Byron.

00:10:12.560 --> 00:10:13.790
And the Lord said, 'I'm going to touch

00:10:13.800 --> 00:10:16.910
his

00:10:16.910 --> 00:10:16.920
life.'I

00:10:16.920 --> 00:10:18.510
saw

00:10:20.000 --> 00:10:24.030
DeSantis was 50/50.

00:10:24.040 --> 00:10:27.230
He was not as good as what he portrays,

00:10:27.240 --> 00:10:31.190
but he was

00:10:31.200 --> 00:10:33.990
a 50/50 mix.

00:10:34.000 --> 00:10:38.390
And the Lord said Rubio was not;

00:10:38.400 --> 00:10:41.630
his heart was more pliable.

00:10:41.640 --> 00:10:44.270
And He said, 'Pray for these men.

00:10:44.280 --> 00:10:46.590
I saw them becoming the cabinet of

00:10:46.600 --> 00:10:48.910
the next

00:10:48.910 --> 00:10:48.920
administration.'That's

00:10:48.920 --> 00:10:50.990
what I was praying for.

00:10:53.240 --> 00:10:55.710
I saw the African-American man.

00:10:55.720 --> 00:10:57.190
People get mad and say,

00:10:57.190 --> 00:10:57.200
'Brandon,

00:10:57.200 --> 00:10:59.190
you say racial

00:10:59.190 --> 00:10:59.200
things.'Listen,

00:10:59.200 --> 00:11:01.190
I'm just a Southern boy. I don't

00:11:01.200 --> 00:11:02.470
know nothing about trying to be

00:11:02.480 --> 00:11:04.910
racist. I love all colors. I love

00:11:04.920 --> 00:11:07.030
blacks, whites,

00:11:07.040 --> 00:11:09.910
Chinese, Asians—I love

00:11:09.920 --> 00:11:11.710
all of you. Brandon Biggs doesn't have

00:11:11.720 --> 00:11:14.070
racism in his bones.

00:11:14.080 --> 00:11:16.070
I love you. It's because I'm trying

00:11:16.080 --> 00:11:17.710
to be politically correct, trying to

00:11:17.720 --> 00:11:19.190
talk in front of hundreds of thousands

00:11:19.200 --> 00:11:21.870
of people, and I may butcher things.

00:11:21.880 --> 00:11:23.070
Then people say, 'Well, we're not

00:11:23.080 --> 00:11:25.190
African-Americans; we're just

00:11:25.190 --> 00:11:25.200
Africans.'Well,

00:11:25.200 --> 00:11:27.430
I'm ignorant, okay? So forgive

00:11:27.440 --> 00:11:28.310
me.

00:11:28.320 --> 00:11:29.670
But I do the best I can with what I

00:11:29.680 --> 00:11:31.470
know.

00:11:31.480 --> 00:11:33.110
I saw this man

00:11:33.120 --> 00:11:35.190
rise up like a vice president in the

00:11:35.200 --> 00:11:37.270
days ahead.

00:11:37.280 --> 00:11:40.390
I saw that there would be a strong pull

00:11:40.400 --> 00:11:42.990
for

00:11:42.990 --> 00:11:43.000
him—this

00:11:43.000 --> 00:11:44.710
man right here. And the

00:11:44.710 --> 00:11:44.720
Lord said,

00:11:44.720 --> 00:11:47.270
'Pray for

00:11:47.270 --> 00:11:47.280
him.'And

00:11:47.280 --> 00:11:48.510
that's when I was talking about the

00:11:48.520 --> 00:11:51.790
restoration and the restitution

00:11:51.800 --> 00:11:55.390
of making wrongs right

00:11:55.400 --> 00:11:57.550
for a true

00:11:58.720 --> 00:12:01.110
African-American who is going

00:12:01.120 --> 00:12:03.270
to rise up.

00:12:03.280 --> 00:12:04.910
And the Lord said, 'I'm going to

00:12:04.920 --> 00:12:06.750
restore back what the

00:12:06.760 --> 00:12:09.550
cankerworm

00:12:09.550 --> 00:12:09.560
ate.'Obama

00:12:09.560 --> 00:12:12.670
had a white mama,

00:12:12.680 --> 00:12:14.310
but he's a true

00:12:14.320 --> 00:12:15.750
black man.

00:12:15.760 --> 00:12:17.030
And the Lord said, 'Watch what I do with

00:12:17.040 --> 00:12:21.350
this

00:12:21.350 --> 00:12:21.360
man.'And

00:12:21.360 --> 00:12:24.750
I saw a blessing on him.

00:12:24.760 --> 00:12:26.350
So you pray for him

00:12:26.360 --> 00:12:28.150
because with that

00:12:28.160 --> 00:12:30.630
target on you

00:12:30.640 --> 00:12:32.790
in the spirit realm, the enemy would

00:12:32.800 --> 00:12:35.550
try to derail it.

00:12:35.560 --> 00:12:37.750
The enemy knows what's being prophesied

00:12:37.760 --> 00:12:39.110
and

00:12:39.120 --> 00:12:41.310
he doesn't want him to succeed.

00:12:41.320 --> 00:12:43.829
So we're going to pray for him.

00:12:43.839 --> 00:12:45.430
We pray for a covering over that man

00:12:45.440 --> 00:12:47.070
Byron,

00:12:47.070 --> 00:12:47.080
just

00:12:47.080 --> 00:12:48.670
like how I told you about President

00:12:48.680 --> 00:12:50.510
Trump.

00:12:50.520 --> 00:12:52.390
God

00:12:52.400 --> 00:12:54.590
has him in the office, and the enemy does not

00:12:54.600 --> 00:12:56.390
want him to fulfill what God has called

00:12:56.400 --> 00:12:58.350
him to do.

00:12:58.360 --> 00:13:00.990
There's a covering over him,

00:13:01.000 --> 00:13:02.790
and He said he must make it across the

00:13:02.800 --> 00:13:06.750
finish line. There

00:13:06.750 --> 00:13:06.760
are

00:13:06.760 --> 00:13:09.150
things that God has appointed

00:13:09.160 --> 00:13:11.350
him to accomplish that have to be

00:13:11.360 --> 00:13:14.670
accomplished, and Cuba is one of them.

00:13:14.680 --> 00:13:16.390
The Lord said, 'I'm going to liberate

00:13:16.400 --> 00:13:18.630
the people.'And I saw old grandmas

00:13:18.640 --> 00:13:20.870
praying. They had prayer shawls. They

00:13:20.880 --> 00:13:23.270
looked like they were Catholic nuns. And

00:13:23.280 --> 00:13:26.310
they were weeping before the Lord as

00:13:26.320 --> 00:13:28.790
there was liberation coming to set the

00:13:28.800 --> 00:13:32.430
people of Cuba free.

00:13:32.440 --> 00:13:34.430
And the Lord said, 'In the days ahead,

00:13:34.440 --> 00:13:36.550
watch. Keep praying

00:13:36.560 --> 00:13:39.470
for what I'm about to do with

00:13:39.480 --> 00:13:40.670
Cuba.'Okay?

00:13:40.680 --> 00:13:42.030
And we keep bringing that up. We keep

00:13:42.040 --> 00:13:42.870
bringing it up, and I said, "It's

00:13:42.880 --> 00:13:43.990
coming."The

00:13:44.000 --> 00:13:45.670
Lord keeps—the visions are very

00:13:45.680 --> 00:13:47.750
colorful. They're very, very vibrant.

00:13:47.760 --> 00:13:48.950
That means they're getting closer and

00:13:48.960 --> 00:13:50.270
closer. There's something about to

00:13:50.280 --> 00:13:51.910
happen. This is why the Lord keeps having us

00:13:51.920 --> 00:13:53.550
pray for this.

00:13:53.560 --> 00:13:55.950
But I saw Taiwan;

00:13:55.960 --> 00:13:58.190
I saw a two-year

00:13:58.200 --> 00:14:00.270
window. Do you remember I told you that

00:14:00.280 --> 00:14:03.790
I heard President Trump

00:14:03.790 --> 00:14:03.800
say—and

00:14:03.800 --> 00:14:05.910
I don't know if this

00:14:05.920 --> 00:14:07.990
was his thoughts, and I don't want

00:14:08.000 --> 00:14:10.750
to be invasive, but I heard it—"All we

00:14:10.760 --> 00:14:12.670
need is two years. We don't need their

00:14:12.680 --> 00:14:15.510
chips. We'll make our own chips.

00:14:15.520 --> 00:14:18.670
We will create chips in America.

00:14:18.680 --> 00:14:21.310
All we need now is two years and

00:14:21.320 --> 00:14:23.510
we will develop our own chips."Do you

00:14:23.520 --> 00:14:24.910
have it?

00:14:24.920 --> 00:14:25.990
Yeah. I don't know if he said all that,

00:14:26.000 --> 00:14:26.950
but yeah. You said

00:14:26.960 --> 00:14:28.830
chips. "We don't

00:14:28.840 --> 00:14:29.870
need..."Yeah.

00:14:29.880 --> 00:14:32.230
Well, I didn't say it because I'm

00:14:32.240 --> 00:14:33.230
trying to be careful.

00:14:33.240 --> 00:14:34.070
Yes.

00:14:34.080 --> 00:14:35.470
So, I'm saying it today.

00:14:37.480 --> 00:14:41.230
So, I saw a two-year window.

00:14:41.240 --> 00:14:42.990
I saw a two-year window. And the Lord

00:14:43.000 --> 00:14:45.710
said, "Do they?"And so I saw why President

00:14:45.720 --> 00:14:48.430
Trump was trying to keep the dragon

00:14:48.440 --> 00:14:51.390
at bay, cracking his whip.

00:14:51.400 --> 00:14:53.829
Okay? I saw China cracking his whip. Like,

00:14:53.839 --> 00:14:54.910
"Listen,"and

00:14:54.920 --> 00:14:56.670
then President Trump said,

00:14:56.680 --> 00:14:58.870
"We're 8,000 or 9,000

00:14:58.870 --> 00:14:58.880
miles

00:14:58.880 --> 00:15:00.430
away.

00:15:00.440 --> 00:15:02.150
We're a long way."That's why I said,

00:15:02.160 --> 00:15:06.070
"Pray for Hawaii.

00:15:06.080 --> 00:15:07.990
Pray for Hawaii

00:15:08.000 --> 00:15:10.270
because I saw a Pearl Harbor event

00:15:10.280 --> 00:15:13.150
taking place in Hawaii

00:15:13.160 --> 00:15:17.510
by China. It was Midway, a mid-ground

00:15:17.520 --> 00:15:19.190
for our bases there

00:15:19.200 --> 00:15:21.190
to go off and try to

00:15:21.200 --> 00:15:24.990
protect. So as I saw that

00:15:25.000 --> 00:15:26.910
protection there, it was a

00:15:26.910 --> 00:15:26.920
two-year

00:15:26.920 --> 00:15:28.310
window—praying

00:15:28.320 --> 00:15:29.950
over a two-year window because the

00:15:29.960 --> 00:15:32.110
Trump

00:15:32.110 --> 00:15:32.120
administration—praying

00:15:32.120 --> 00:15:34.590
over his covering over

00:15:34.590 --> 00:15:34.600
him—it

00:15:34.600 --> 00:15:37.670
has about two and a half years left. So

00:15:37.680 --> 00:15:39.510
what we would have left of what I'm

00:15:39.520 --> 00:15:45.230
seeing, what we're praying over, is

00:15:45.240 --> 00:15:46.910
China taking it, but we would have our

00:15:46.920 --> 00:15:48.350
own chips. And that was him

00:15:48.360 --> 00:15:50.350
manufacturing here in

00:15:50.360 --> 00:15:51.870
America:

00:15:51.880 --> 00:15:54.590
Texas, probably Oklahoma, whatever in

00:15:54.600 --> 00:15:56.670
the southern states

00:15:56.680 --> 00:15:58.350
where we're not crazy like some of the

00:15:58.360 --> 00:16:00.390
Democratic states are

00:16:00.400 --> 00:16:02.870
charging so many taxes.

00:16:04.560 --> 00:16:06.470
So that's what we're

00:16:06.470 --> 00:16:06.480
trying

00:16:06.480 --> 00:16:07.590
to play or not because it's a

00:16:07.600 --> 00:16:09.150
distraction.

00:16:09.160 --> 00:16:10.150
Go ahead.

00:16:10.160 --> 00:16:11.590
Well, yeah. When I see it spinning,

00:16:11.600 --> 00:16:13.230
Trump

00:16:14.550 --> 00:16:14.560
wants

00:16:16.280 --> 00:16:18.830
to pull back and he'll

00:16:18.840 --> 00:16:21.830
start to focus on this.

00:16:21.840 --> 00:16:24.110
Oh,

00:16:24.120 --> 00:16:27.270
and I see Taiwan in the midst of it.

00:16:27.280 --> 00:16:30.150
I see Taiwan in the midst of it

00:16:30.160 --> 00:16:33.270
bartering pieces. Do you understand?

00:16:33.270 --> 00:16:33.280
Trump's

00:16:33.280 --> 00:16:37.910
going to make his own chips.

00:16:37.920 --> 00:16:39.630
Do you hear?

00:16:39.640 --> 00:16:41.950
Trump's going to make his own chips.

00:16:41.960 --> 00:16:43.670
We don't need Taiwan.

00:16:43.680 --> 00:16:44.750
That's what he...

00:16:44.760 --> 00:16:46.870
and I don't mean that trying to—Chapter 2: Find

00:16:46.870 --> 00:16:46.880
scriptures to stand on—I'm

00:16:46.880 --> 00:16:51.390
just telling you what I heard. I see it.

00:16:51.400 --> 00:16:53.310
We pray for the people of Taiwan. That's

00:16:53.320 --> 00:16:56.350
what we got to do.

00:16:56.360 --> 00:16:58.950
I'm just called

00:16:58.950 --> 00:16:58.960
to

00:16:58.960 --> 00:17:09.230
fear God, not man.

00:17:09.240 --> 00:17:11.630
So I got quiet because the Lord

00:17:11.630 --> 00:17:11.640
rebuked

00:17:11.640 --> 00:17:12.870
me right there

00:17:12.880 --> 00:17:15.189
and he said, "You fear me, not

00:17:15.189 --> 00:17:15.199
them."Because

00:17:15.199 --> 00:17:16.990
I was concerned about what Taiwan

00:17:17.000 --> 00:17:19.069
people would be saying because of

00:17:19.079 --> 00:17:20.949
what Trump had—about what he said. And

00:17:20.959 --> 00:17:22.710
so that's why I was correcting that

00:17:22.720 --> 00:17:24.429
because in my heart, I was thinking

00:17:24.439 --> 00:17:26.150
more about what they were

00:17:26.160 --> 00:17:27.590
thinking than the prophetic

00:17:27.600 --> 00:17:28.910
word of what the Lord was showing me,

00:17:28.920 --> 00:17:30.190
saying,

00:17:30.200 --> 00:17:31.750
"Trump, this is what Trump said: 'We don't

00:17:31.760 --> 00:17:33.750
need Taiwan.

00:17:33.760 --> 00:17:35.710
We have our own chips. All we need is

00:17:35.720 --> 00:17:37.630
two years.

00:17:37.640 --> 00:17:40.070
All we need is two years.'"And then I was

00:17:40.080 --> 00:17:42.350
more feeling about the people's feelings.

00:17:42.360 --> 00:17:43.830
And the Lord said,

00:17:43.840 --> 00:17:47.630
"Fear me, not them."And he corrected me.

00:17:47.640 --> 00:17:48.990
I'm just being real. That's what was

00:17:49.000 --> 00:17:50.550
going on right there. I got rebuked

00:17:50.560 --> 00:17:54.470
again right then.

00:17:55.840 --> 00:17:58.510
So the Lord showed us more about that.

00:17:58.520 --> 00:18:00.750
Now, this is what was said about Taiwan

00:18:00.760 --> 00:18:02.470
today and President Trump just had this

00:18:02.480 --> 00:18:05.110
meeting.

00:18:05.120 --> 00:18:05.510
Go ahead.

00:18:05.510 --> 00:18:05.520
But

00:18:05.520 --> 00:18:08.310
China made clear that Taiwan is very

00:18:08.320 --> 00:18:10.430
important to them. And after your first

00:18:10.440 --> 00:18:12.750
meeting here, President Xi's spokesman

00:18:12.760 --> 00:18:14.310
put out a statement to the media

00:18:14.320 --> 00:18:16.230
saying this: "The Taiwan

00:18:16.240 --> 00:18:17.830
question is the most important issue in

00:18:17.840 --> 00:18:19.790
China-US relations. If it is handled

00:18:19.800 --> 00:18:22.110
properly, the bilateral relationship will

00:18:22.120 --> 00:18:24.150
enjoy overall stability. Otherwise, the

00:18:24.160 --> 00:18:26.430
two countries will have clashes and even

00:18:26.440 --> 00:18:27.950
conflicts, putting the entire

00:18:27.960 --> 00:18:30.670
relationship in great jeopardy."You were

00:18:30.680 --> 00:18:32.150
still inside the meeting when that came

00:18:32.160 --> 00:18:34.750
out. That sounded almost like a threat.

00:18:34.760 --> 00:18:36.830
Was it communicated that way

00:18:36.840 --> 00:18:37.830
behind closed doors?

00:18:37.840 --> 00:18:39.870
No. And no, it wasn't. Not at all. But it

00:18:39.880 --> 00:18:41.310
has always been their most important

00:18:41.320 --> 00:18:42.510
issue.

00:18:42.520 --> 00:18:44.710
And it's not a takeover. They just don't

00:18:44.720 --> 00:18:46.390
want to see this

00:18:46.400 --> 00:18:46.990
place—we'll

00:18:47.000 --> 00:18:49.030
call it a place because nobody

00:18:49.040 --> 00:18:51.110
knows how to define it—but they don't

00:18:51.120 --> 00:18:52.990
want to see it go independent. They

00:18:53.000 --> 00:18:55.470
don't want to do it. And

00:18:55.480 --> 00:18:56.870
I think they probably would do

00:18:56.880 --> 00:18:58.470
something pretty harsh and then they

00:18:58.480 --> 00:19:00.710
would be met harshly and bad things will

00:19:00.720 --> 00:19:01.750
happen.

00:19:01.760 --> 00:19:03.150
So

00:19:03.160 --> 00:19:05.550
no, it's not that. We talked, by

00:19:05.560 --> 00:19:06.990
the way—last night we talked a whole

00:19:07.000 --> 00:19:09.630
night about that issue. I think I

00:19:09.640 --> 00:19:11.350
know more about Taiwan right now than I

00:19:11.360 --> 00:19:13.630
know about almost any country.

00:19:13.640 --> 00:19:14.390
He

00:19:14.400 --> 00:19:15.350
dominated

00:19:15.360 --> 00:19:16.190
the talk.

00:19:16.200 --> 00:19:18.470
It's always been his most

00:19:18.480 --> 00:19:20.310
important thing from the day I knew him

00:19:20.320 --> 00:19:22.630
years ago. I've known him now 11,

00:19:22.640 --> 00:19:23.950
12 years.

00:19:23.960 --> 00:19:25.310
It's always been the biggest thing

00:19:25.320 --> 00:19:27.830
for him: Taiwan. Now

00:19:27.840 --> 00:19:29.110
with me, I don't think they'll do

00:19:29.120 --> 00:19:30.870
anything when I'm here.

00:19:30.880 --> 00:19:32.670
When I'm not here, I think they might,

00:19:32.680 --> 00:19:34.830
to be honest with you. So, I'm not sure

00:19:34.840 --> 00:19:37.110
that they do anything if it remained as

00:19:37.120 --> 00:19:38.230
is,

00:19:38.240 --> 00:19:39.830
but they have somebody there now that

00:19:39.840 --> 00:19:41.670
wants to go independent. Well, it's

00:19:41.670 --> 00:19:41.680
a

00:19:41.680 --> 00:19:42.830
risky thing when you go

00:19:42.840 --> 00:19:44.190
independent. You know, they're going

00:19:44.200 --> 00:19:45.710
independent because they want to get into a

00:19:45.720 --> 00:19:47.630
war and they want to—they figure they

00:19:47.640 --> 00:19:49.910
have the United States behind them.

00:19:50.480 --> 00:19:52.230
I'd like to see it stay the way it is.

00:19:52.240 --> 00:19:54.030
And I'll tell you something, I'll make a

00:19:54.040 --> 00:19:55.710
little news. I'd like to see everybody

00:19:55.720 --> 00:19:57.670
making chips over in Taiwan come

00:19:57.670 --> 00:19:57.680
to

00:19:57.680 --> 00:19:59.190
America because, to be honest with you, I

00:19:59.200 --> 00:20:00.510
think it's the greatest thing you can

00:20:00.520 --> 00:20:01.630
do

00:20:01.630 --> 00:20:01.640
because

00:20:01.640 --> 00:20:03.310
it's a heated situation. There's no

00:20:03.320 --> 00:20:05.790
question about it. And

00:20:05.800 --> 00:20:08.030
as you know, we have massive amounts of

00:20:08.040 --> 00:20:10.350
chip companies now from Taiwan already

00:20:10.360 --> 00:20:13.310
coming in. We expect to have 40 to 50%

00:20:13.320 --> 00:20:15.310
of the world chip business by the end of

00:20:15.320 --> 00:20:16.470
my term.

00:20:16.480 --> 00:20:18.470
And I think it should be even more

00:20:18.480 --> 00:20:20.350
than that. I think all of those chip

00:20:20.350 --> 00:20:20.360
companies—if

00:20:20.360 --> 00:20:22.550
they're smart, they're

00:20:22.560 --> 00:20:24.030
going to start heading to Arizona and

00:20:24.040 --> 00:20:25.470
the places where they're building.

00:20:25.480 --> 00:20:28.950
That's going to solve your problem.

00:20:28.960 --> 00:20:31.110
So do you see that? It's what we saw in

00:20:31.120 --> 00:20:32.550
the spirit.

00:20:32.560 --> 00:20:33.750
That was what I was seeing. And

00:20:33.760 --> 00:20:35.230
then they had the meeting and they had

00:20:35.240 --> 00:20:37.030
this interview,

00:20:37.040 --> 00:20:38.030
and this is what the Lord said: "We

00:20:38.040 --> 00:20:39.870
don't need

00:20:39.870 --> 00:20:39.880
Taiwan."That's

00:20:39.880 --> 00:20:41.390
what he was saying. "We have

00:20:41.400 --> 00:20:42.990
our own

00:20:42.990 --> 00:20:43.000
chips."And

00:20:43.000 --> 00:20:44.750
that was the whole reason why

00:20:44.760 --> 00:20:46.550
America was back in Taiwan.

00:20:46.560 --> 00:20:49.270
And they were moving into America.

00:20:49.280 --> 00:20:50.510
And that's why I said, "Pray for

00:20:50.520 --> 00:20:52.350
Taiwan,"because

00:20:52.360 --> 00:20:54.790
I saw them

00:20:54.790 --> 00:20:54.800
being—I

00:20:54.800 --> 00:20:57.950
saw a mother hen bringing

00:20:57.960 --> 00:21:00.630
the island to her,

00:21:00.640 --> 00:21:03.390
trying to infiltrate South Korea

00:21:03.400 --> 00:21:05.670
through the politics, through North

00:21:05.680 --> 00:21:06.990
Korea,

00:21:07.000 --> 00:21:07.910
through

00:21:07.920 --> 00:21:10.470
the Philippines, through all

00:21:10.480 --> 00:21:13.270
of Japan, trying to bring them in like a

00:21:13.280 --> 00:21:16.070
mother hen.

00:21:16.080 --> 00:21:17.470
And that's why I warned

00:21:17.470 --> 00:21:17.480
you—how

00:21:17.480 --> 00:21:19.030
many times do you remember me

00:21:19.040 --> 00:21:20.590
saying this? They said, "Watch what China

00:21:20.590 --> 00:21:20.600
does."And

00:21:20.600 --> 00:21:23.070
I saw

00:21:23.080 --> 00:21:27.270
China turning their back on the

00:21:27.270 --> 00:21:27.280
Ukraine-Russia

00:21:27.280 --> 00:21:29.670
thing that's going on.

00:21:29.680 --> 00:21:32.390
And I saw—remember I said I see a panda

00:21:32.400 --> 00:21:35.510
bear? Then I saw a turtle. I saw a dove

00:21:35.520 --> 00:21:38.270
with a wounded chest. I saw two black

00:21:38.280 --> 00:21:40.750
crows.

00:21:40.760 --> 00:21:42.790
I saw

00:21:42.800 --> 00:21:44.990
a robin,

00:21:45.000 --> 00:21:47.710
and the robin had wounded the dove.

00:21:47.720 --> 00:21:49.590
The two black crows were standing there

00:21:49.600 --> 00:21:51.430
by the dove, and they were looking at the

00:21:51.440 --> 00:21:53.590
dove that was perished on the ground

00:21:53.600 --> 00:21:57.110
with its heart ripped out.

00:21:57.120 --> 00:21:59.830
And I said this is symbolic of people.

00:21:59.840 --> 00:22:01.710
And I saw the panda

00:22:01.720 --> 00:22:06.710
turn its back upon Russia and Ukraine,

00:22:06.720 --> 00:22:09.150
and I said he was gazing towards Taiwan,

00:22:09.160 --> 00:22:10.910
and it said, "It's our time. We want to

00:22:10.920 --> 00:22:12.870
take Taiwan now."And

00:22:12.870 --> 00:22:12.880
Xi Jinping

00:22:12.880 --> 00:22:14.230
is talking about it, and that's all

00:22:14.240 --> 00:22:15.870
they're talking about. That was three weeks

00:22:15.880 --> 00:22:16.910
ago,

00:22:16.910 --> 00:22:16.920
two

00:22:16.920 --> 00:22:18.950
weeks ago at the most. Maybe it was

00:22:18.960 --> 00:22:20.430
last week.

00:22:20.440 --> 00:22:21.670
And I said, "You're going to see an

00:22:21.680 --> 00:22:24.270
acceleration concerning Taiwan in the

00:22:24.280 --> 00:22:26.870
days ahead. Pray over Taiwan.

00:22:26.870 --> 00:22:26.880
Watch."And

00:22:26.880 --> 00:22:29.310
now this is all

00:22:29.310 --> 00:22:29.320
they're—"Are

00:22:29.320 --> 00:22:30.510
you going to stand in our way if we

00:22:30.520 --> 00:22:33.830
do

00:22:33.830 --> 00:22:33.840
this?"Okay.

00:22:33.840 --> 00:22:37.630
But I saw as we took Cuba and

00:22:37.640 --> 00:22:40.230
liberated Cuba and made them prosperous

00:22:40.240 --> 00:22:42.990
and blessed and got rid of the

00:22:43.000 --> 00:22:45.910
government they have and set up hotels

00:22:45.920 --> 00:22:48.190
and churches and blessing. That's why

00:22:48.190 --> 00:22:48.200
we are

00:22:48.200 --> 00:22:50.630
praying for certain pastors in Miami,

00:22:50.630 --> 00:22:50.640
because they

00:22:50.640 --> 00:22:52.150
are

00:22:52.160 --> 00:22:53.270
already setting up. They're already

00:22:53.280 --> 00:22:54.590
walking by faith. They know what's

00:22:54.600 --> 00:22:55.870
coming.

00:22:55.880 --> 00:22:57.470
I've talked to them on the phone;

00:22:57.480 --> 00:23:00.270
they already know what's coming. God

00:23:00.280 --> 00:23:03.830
is about to do something huge in Cuba.

00:23:03.840 --> 00:23:05.390
So you don't wait until it

00:23:05.400 --> 00:23:07.950
happens. You're

00:23:07.960 --> 00:23:09.110
not going to be reactive; you're

00:23:09.120 --> 00:23:11.150
proactive, right? So you're already

00:23:11.160 --> 00:23:13.110
getting your stuff ready because you

00:23:13.120 --> 00:23:14.750
know what God's about to do in this

00:23:14.760 --> 00:23:17.110
end-time move.

00:23:17.120 --> 00:23:18.190
You're not going to wait until it

00:23:18.200 --> 00:23:20.630
happens, because then you're already too late. You

00:23:20.640 --> 00:23:21.990
want to be the forerunners for the

00:23:22.000 --> 00:23:24.350
greatest move of God we've ever seen in

00:23:24.360 --> 00:23:27.030
this

00:23:27.030 --> 00:23:27.040
modern-day

00:23:27.040 --> 00:23:29.150
era.

00:23:29.160 --> 00:23:31.070
Watch what God is about to do with the

00:23:31.080 --> 00:23:34.790
greatest revival. Ladies and gentlemen,

00:23:34.800 --> 00:23:37.350
I'm just excited to be a part of it.

00:23:37.360 --> 00:23:38.990
Go ahead and play the video concerning

00:23:39.000 --> 00:23:40.910
Cuba. Did you find anything about that,

00:23:40.920 --> 00:23:41.950
son?

00:23:41.960 --> 00:23:43.110
Was the panda bear

00:23:43.960 --> 00:23:45.030
talking about that?

00:23:45.040 --> 00:23:49.630
Okay, this is the panda bear.

00:23:49.640 --> 00:23:50.750
When was that?

00:23:52.360 --> 00:24:02.630
April 30th, two weeks ago.

00:24:02.640 --> 00:24:07.590
The panda bear

00:24:13.600 --> 00:24:15.510
is devising a plan

00:24:15.520 --> 00:24:21.150
of its own

00:24:21.150 --> 00:24:21.160
with

00:24:21.160 --> 00:24:25.030
a box.

00:24:25.040 --> 00:24:27.990
The panda bear

00:24:28.000 --> 00:24:32.230
has a box

00:24:32.240 --> 00:24:34.150
and is looking over because he doesn't

00:24:34.160 --> 00:24:36.390
want you to see it.

00:24:36.400 --> 00:24:38.470
He has his head down and he's

00:24:38.480 --> 00:24:41.230
looking in the box,

00:24:41.240 --> 00:24:50.990
but he has a plan of his own.

00:24:51.000 --> 00:24:54.430
He's turning his back on Putin;

00:24:54.440 --> 00:24:56.310
he's turning his back on everyone else

00:24:56.320 --> 00:24:59.710
and has a plan by himself.

00:24:59.720 --> 00:25:14.110
The

00:25:14.120 --> 00:25:18.390
evil-looking panda

00:25:18.390 --> 00:25:18.400
is

00:25:18.400 --> 00:25:23.510
wrapped in their flag

00:25:23.520 --> 00:25:30.190
and it's talking to the dragon

00:25:30.200 --> 00:25:31.510
Kim

00:25:37.190 --> 00:25:37.200
Jong-un

00:25:39.160 --> 00:25:42.990
as they gaze upon Taiwan. Do you see?

00:25:43.000 --> 00:25:45.230
I said, 'Yeah, they gaze upon it.'Taiwan

00:25:45.230 --> 00:25:45.240
is

00:25:45.240 --> 00:25:48.270
glowing with

00:25:48.280 --> 00:25:58.110
yellow lights.

00:25:58.120 --> 00:26:02.070
And the panda is licking its lips.

00:26:02.080 --> 00:26:05.670
The panda is licking its

00:26:05.670 --> 00:26:05.680
lips—his

00:26:05.680 --> 00:26:07.550
big long tongue—and he's licking

00:26:07.560 --> 00:26:14.910
his lips.

00:26:19.920 --> 00:26:28.030
Well, praise the Lord.

00:26:28.040 --> 00:26:29.910
Father, we just praise you tonight

00:26:29.920 --> 00:26:33.070
for what you've shown us.

00:26:33.080 --> 00:26:34.670
Lord, we thank you

00:26:34.680 --> 00:26:35.670
that we will pray over this and continue to

00:26:35.680 --> 00:26:36.990
pray over this.

00:26:37.000 --> 00:26:39.390
That's when he stopped;

00:26:39.400 --> 00:26:40.870
that's why I stopped

00:26:40.870 --> 00:26:40.880
and

00:26:40.880 --> 00:26:44.470
started.

00:26:44.480 --> 00:26:48.510
Thank you, Lord. Right now, son,

00:26:48.520 --> 00:26:50.350
it's a good number. Always pray

00:26:50.360 --> 00:26:52.670
with me; there is so much more time.

00:26:53.520 --> 00:26:54.910
That's when it lifted,

00:26:54.920 --> 00:26:56.150
because I said they

00:26:56.160 --> 00:26:57.190
were licking their lips. They're about to

