of the Gerber babies.

00:49:01.800 --> 00:49:03.190
And it had big chubby cheeks, you

00:49:03.190 --> 00:49:03.200
know."And

00:49:03.200 --> 00:49:04.590
I said, "That baby looked pretty,

00:49:04.600 --> 00:49:06.070
but the baby Israel didn't look too

00:49:06.070 --> 00:49:06.080
pretty."I

00:49:06.080 --> 00:49:08.310
said, "I don't know why. I'm

00:49:08.320 --> 00:49:09.630
not trying to be mean. I'm just being

00:49:09.630 --> 00:49:09.640
real."It

00:49:09.640 --> 00:49:11.550
had really curly

00:49:11.560 --> 00:49:13.470
looking hair and it had a big

00:49:13.480 --> 00:49:15.750
tooth. I don't know how many infants

00:49:15.760 --> 00:49:17.270
have teeth,

00:49:17.280 --> 00:49:19.870
but this infant did;

00:49:19.870 --> 00:49:19.880
it

00:49:19.880 --> 00:49:22.270
had a big front tooth.

00:49:22.280 --> 00:49:24.270
Looked like a rabbit. I

00:49:24.280 --> 00:49:25.870
thought, "What in the world is going on

00:49:25.880 --> 00:49:28.030
with that rabbit tooth on that

00:49:28.030 --> 00:49:28.040
baby?"It

00:49:28.040 --> 00:49:30.070
was an infant that had teeth

00:49:30.080 --> 00:49:31.430
already.

00:49:31.440 --> 00:49:33.390
So, whatever that's about, I don't know.

00:49:33.400 --> 00:49:34.670
The visions

00:49:34.680 --> 00:49:35.950
what the Lord shows me are kind of funny.

00:49:35.960 --> 00:49:37.190
Sometimes I laugh about them after they

00:49:37.190 --> 00:49:37.200
are

00:49:37.200 --> 00:49:39.550
over. I go, "What was that, Lord?

00:49:39.560 --> 00:49:41.910
Why did I see a baby with a

00:49:41.920 --> 00:49:44.190
tooth in his mouth, with curly hair,

00:49:44.200 --> 00:49:45.670
with a little bow up there, and it said

00:49:45.680 --> 00:49:47.670
Israel flag? Then I saw America and it

00:49:47.680 --> 00:49:49.350
looked real cute like a little Gerber

00:49:49.350 --> 00:49:49.360
baby."And

00:49:49.360 --> 00:49:51.350
I thought, "Well, that baby in

00:49:51.360 --> 00:49:54.110
Israel didn't look too pretty;

00:49:54.120 --> 00:49:57.430
kind of an ugly baby."But okay.

00:50:00.640 --> 00:50:01.870
So, all right, well, we're going to

00:50:01.880 --> 00:50:03.310
pray. Father, we just thank you for the

00:50:03.320 --> 00:50:05.150
word. We thank you, Father, for the

00:50:05.160 --> 00:50:07.590
body that was—that you died for us.

00:50:07.600 --> 00:50:10.230
You suffered for us. We're so grateful

00:50:10.240 --> 00:50:12.270
for all that you've done. We're so

00:50:12.280 --> 00:50:14.790
grateful that you died on the cross for

00:50:14.800 --> 00:50:18.910
all of us. And we live by faith and not

00:50:18.920 --> 00:50:21.110
by sight. We're not moved by what we

00:50:21.120 --> 00:50:23.350
see. We're not moved by what we feel.

00:50:23.360 --> 00:50:25.110
We're moved by what the word of God

00:50:25.120 --> 00:50:28.030
says. And if God be for us, who can be

00:50:28.040 --> 00:50:31.150
against us? Greater is he that is in

00:50:31.160 --> 00:50:33.390
me than he that is in the world. A

00:50:33.400 --> 00:50:36.190
thousand shall fall at my side and

00:50:36.200 --> 00:50:38.390
10,000 at my right hand, but nothing

00:50:38.400 --> 00:50:40.670
shall come nigh us. The greater one

00:50:40.680 --> 00:50:43.270
lives on the inside of me.

00:50:43.280 --> 00:50:46.430
I'm wall-to-wall Holy Ghost.

00:50:46.440 --> 00:50:48.830
And if he did it, we can do it because

00:50:48.840 --> 00:50:53.150
as he is, so are we in this world. And I

00:50:53.160 --> 00:50:55.310
thank you, Lord, for the body. And I

00:50:55.320 --> 00:50:57.350
thank you, God, for what you did. And I

00:50:57.360 --> 00:50:59.350
receive it by faith in the name of

00:50:59.360 --> 00:51:05.630
Jesus.

00:51:05.640 --> 00:51:07.830
Lord, we plead the blood and we make

00:51:07.840 --> 00:51:09.670
much of the blood, and the blood makes

00:51:09.680 --> 00:51:12.710
much of us. We apply the blood over us

00:51:12.720 --> 00:51:15.350
in Jesus'name and it never loses its

00:51:15.360 --> 00:51:18.150
power. We apply the blood over our

00:51:18.160 --> 00:51:20.790
minds. We apply the blood over

00:51:20.800 --> 00:51:22.710
our prayer time tonight,

00:51:22.720 --> 00:51:24.870
uninterrupted and unhindered by any

00:51:24.880 --> 00:51:28.750
satanic or demonic force. We plead the

00:51:28.760 --> 00:51:30.590
blood. And if you want to show us

00:51:30.600 --> 00:51:33.670
anything, Lord, we yield. We yield to

00:51:33.680 --> 00:51:35.070
the anointing of the watcher. We yield

00:51:35.080 --> 00:51:36.590
to the anointing of the prophetic. And

00:51:36.600 --> 00:51:38.110
Father, I thank you, Lord, that we see

00:51:38.120 --> 00:51:39.910
that which is to come,

00:51:39.920 --> 00:51:42.150
uninterrupted and unhindered by any

00:51:42.160 --> 00:51:45.550
satanic or demonic force. We apply the

00:51:45.560 --> 00:51:48.710
blood of Jesus. And greater is he, we

00:51:48.720 --> 00:51:50.470
say it all the time,

00:51:50.480 --> 00:51:52.070
that is in me than he that is in the

00:51:52.080 --> 00:51:53.350
world.

00:51:53.360 --> 00:51:55.310
Amen and amen. We plead the blood of

00:51:55.320 --> 00:51:58.430
Jesus. Amen.

00:51:58.440 --> 00:52:03.150
All right,

00:52:03.160 --> 00:52:04.270
I'm just going to jump right in that

00:52:04.280 --> 00:52:05.710
